content: Lukapetro: Merged three significant plugin-related PRs this week (#1761, #1812, #1773) adding support for CoinGecko, Binance, and CoinMarketCap, with substantial code changes totaling over +4.5k/-1.3k lines. Contributed 13 commits across 88 modified files, primarily focusing on feature work (62%) and bugfixes (31%), with activity concentrated on just 2 days of the week. Also provided one review with comments on another contributor's work.
